"parameters. While the base technology is there, enabling it is a painful and"
" complex process. The goal of this project is to integrate configuration of "
"this feature into Qubes, automating as much as possible. See discussion in "
"`issue #4371 <https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-issues/issues/4371>`__"
msgstr ""

